data.description: "Welcome to your dream home! This cozy 3-bed, 2-bath retreat is flooded with natural light, creating a warm and inviting ambiance. The new roof, AC (2019) guarantee year-round comfort, while the backyard oasis beckons for relaxation by the pool, spa, and beneath the charming pergola amidst lush greenery. The front yard, with its zen-inspired design, adds an extra touch of serenity. Imagine a home with new appliances that elevate your lifestyle. Nestled in a quiet and secure neighborhood, this is the place where your dreams come to life. Don't miss the chance to make this dreamy retreat yours! Contact us today to schedule a visit and experience the charm, comfort, safety, and the added features of brand new gutters that define this home."
